  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0ed7cf1afef16b04ba80aa31ef6d007e, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "So anyway, I want to help create a new world, one where there is no
    inequality, where no child will have to suffer like I did. To that end, it\u2019s
    super important that we ruin the current state of creation. I have one single
    idea, which I think will prove beneficial to us all.. Will burning books cause
    a non-problematic definition of peace? "
